ng wire is 4.3. This result provides useful\ndesign criteria for three-omega experiments by setting a lower bound for the\nmaximum ratio of thermal penetration depth to wire radius of curvature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 May 2020 18:44:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-09"}
