ed as the conjugate footpoints of\nthe erupting flux rope. These observations are broadly consistent with the\nmagnetic topology and the associated energy release scenario suggested in the\nthree-dimensional standard model for eruptive solar flares. In particular, our\ndetection of nonthermal emission at conjugate flux rope footpoints provides\nsolid evidence of particle transport along an erupting magnetic flux rope.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 May 2020 01:21:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 May 2020 18:14:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-10"}
